exceptions.exn: Unable to find an instance for the variables A, a.

exceptions.tactic: destruct (not_in_cons nat v a (freeVarTerm LNN (natToTerm a))); auto.
exceptions.exn: In environment a, v : nat IHa : ~ In v (freeVarTerm LNN (natToTerm a)) The term "v" has type "nat" while it is expected to have type "Set".

original: intros a v. induction a. - simpl. apply in_nil. - simpl. destruct (not_in_cons nat v a (freeVarTerm LNN (natToTerm a))); auto. apply IHa.
